com.coveros.selenified.services

Class Verify

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.coveros.selenified.services.Verify

  • public class Verify
extends Object
    Verify will handle all verifications performed on the actual web services calls themselves. These asserts are custom to the framework, and in addition to providing easy object oriented capabilities, they assist in troubleshooting and debugging failing tests.
    Version:
    3.2.0
    Author:
    Max Saperstone
